    DSPOCtrl -->|"provisions MLMD"| MLMD
    KubeRayCtrl -->|"manages RayCluster<br/>head + worker pods"| RayClusters
    ModelRegOp -->|"creates ModelRegistry<br/>+ PostgreSQL"| ModelRegInst

