    PipelineRuns -->|"status sync"| DSPServer
    LLMDStack -->|"scheduled inference<br/>reverse proxy to vLLM"| InfSvcPods
    MaaSProxy -->|"translated request<br/>injected API key"| ExtLLMProviders

